{"fadeType":2,"once":true,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"sequence":[["Centaur and the Port \"Elders\"\n\n<size=45>Chapter 4 - Unexpected Developments<\/size>",1]]},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"say":"Port - Office","dir":1,"bgm":"story-1","side":2,"bgmDelay":2,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_task","flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Centaur, come play house with us! Kisaragi wants you to play too!","actor":301320,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":0,"time":0.5},"say":"Yes. Even though I don't like planes, I like you, Centaur... Won't you play with me...?","dir":1,"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":301330},{"expression":3,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Oh, but of course I shall.","dir":-1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":206040},{"flashout":{"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Centaur, did you forget you promised to play hide and seek with us?","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":1.5,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":101240},{"expression":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":1,"time":0.5},"say":"Certainly not, Elder Sims, I've been looking forward to it.","dir":-1,"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":206040},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"C'mon, let's go! Hammann is getting all pouty.","actor":101240,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"flashout":{"dur":0.5,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Um, 'scuse me, Commander... I'm lookin' for Centaur. She was gonna rehearse with me...","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"delay":1.5,"dur":0.5,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":201100},{"expression":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":1,"time":0.5},"say":"Yes, Elder Cygnet, you go on ahead. I'll be along shortly.","dir":-1,"side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":206040},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"Cheers. I've got a feelin' we'll have a lot more confidence with you there, Centaur. Don't forget now.","actor":201100,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"I wasn't sure why, but once everyone heard about Centaur's little \"Elder\" quirk, she quickly grew popular among the destroyers.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","options":[{"flag":1,"content":"Ask about her popularity."}]},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"I simply told the destroyer Elders my feelings, and they welcomed me with open arms.","actor":206040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"say":"The destroyer Elders are truly kindhearted.","actor":206040,"dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"...You're so lucky... How is it that my heartfelt, impassioned feelings still go unrequited...","dir":1,"blackBg":true,"actorName":"???","nameColor":"#a9f548"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"A cold, mature voice seething with jealousy emerged from parts unknown.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"...Although I didn't see her approach, I knew all this talk of destroyers would naturally summon one particular individual.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task"},{"expression":2,"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Oh, Elder Ark Royal, good morning!","dir":1,"side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_task","actor":206040},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"Yes. That one.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","blackBg":true}],"mode":2,"fadein":1.5,"id":"BANRENMA4","fadeOut":1.5}